professor of pediatrics at the university of minnesota medical 
school 
polio paralysis results only from about one out of every 32 
million doses of oral polio vaccine he said 
in another example about one in 110000 children who get the 
diphtheriatetanuspertussis dtp vaccine develop a brain 
dysfunction that can include seizures it is usually temporary 
only about one in 310000 vaccinated children suffer permanent 
