jan 4 1954 responding to the research cigarette companies 
take out newspaper advertisements contending cigarettes are safe 
1955 mrs cipollone switches to lampm a liggett brand 
1964 the surgeon general issues his first report linking 
cancer and other diseases to cigarettes 
1966 federal law requires warnings on cigarette packs 
1968 mrs cipollone switches to virginia slims a morris brand 
1971 cigarette advertising banned from television and radio 
mrs cipollone switches to parliament a morris brand 
