gubernatorial campaign which had a theme of integrity and 
abolishing special interests 
along came a pot of gold in the form of barry wolfson and 
evan mecham wound up selling that theme of integrity and ridding 
the state of hidden special interests when he and willard mecham 
decided to hide from the public the 350000 loan cudahy said 
