at 7180 cents a pound feeder cattle were 65 cent to 1 cent lower 
with august at 7327 cents a pound hogs were 105 cents lower to 
43 cent higher with june at 5065 cents a pound frozen pork 
bellies were 1 cent to 188 cents lower with july at 4647 cents a 
pound 
