new york reflecting improved availability of the metal analysts 
said copper for june delivery settled 365 cents lower at 1085 a 
pound 
gold and silver futures posted slight gains in reaction to 
higher grain and energy futures prices 
gold settled 20 cents to 1 higher with august at 45460 a troy 
ounce silver was 06 cent to 15 cents higher with july at 707 a 
troy ounce 
